    "id": 3008,
    "title": "Problem 3008",
    "description": "Write a Python function called `magic_string_value` that must format an object as Value(value) with __str__. Use magic method syntax.\nDifficulty: Easy.\nExamples:\n  magic_string_value(3) -> \"Value(3)\"\n  magic_string_value(-2) -> \"Value(-2)\"",
    "initialCode": "def magic_string_value(value):\n    pass",
